[[zoom-window|https://github.com/syohex/emacs-zoom-window]] provides window zoom like tmux zoom and unzoom.

I have it configured thusly.

```
(require 'zoom-window)
(global-set-key (kbd "C-x C-z") 'zoom-window-zoom)
```

